		<outline text="June 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="june2021" >
			<outline text="June 27" type="calendarDay" name="27" >
				<outline text="I used to read biographies as a kid, loved reading the stories of great people. 

Now I have trouble getting through them, because I know the truth and the stories in the biographies are not that. 

As a kid I reveled in gullibility." type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 17:43:02 GMT" tweetId="1409205645237161988" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1409205645237161988" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="A slogan for programmers. &quot;Let's see what happens.&quot; 

An idea pops into your head. I wonder if that could possibly work? Go for it." type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 17:27:57 GMT" tweetId="1409201851011063812" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1409201851011063812" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
					<outline text="Other kinds of product designers, engineers, or screen writers, don't have the luxury we have. Usually we can try something out and see what happens, and if it blows up, you can shrug and say well I guess it doesn't work. Or maybe it does." type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 17:27:57 GMT" tweetId="1409201851782815745" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1409201851782815745" inReplyToId="1409201851011063812" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
						<outline text="Or maybe in its failure it'll give you and idea of what might work. But be careful not to risk actual data." type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 17:27:58 GMT" tweetId="1409201852814708743" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1409201852814708743" inReplyToId="1409201851782815745" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="I keep getting emails from the Lincoln Project and I want to say to them in a way they can hear -- disband and join  another cause. LP expired after the 2020 election. That was the last chance for Repub voters to save their souls. I do not want leadership from former Repubs." type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 16:03:20 GMT" tweetId="1409180556613537798" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1409180556613537798" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="If the Dems played as hard as the Repubs (they should) they'd be running ads in Florida with live images of the crashed building saying:

&quot;This is where 25 years of Republican leadership has gotten you.&quot;

