						<outline text="PS: For most of the last 26 years I've been writing my blog in an outliner. I'm glad that other people are interested in this now. Let's build a new community around this idea. ;-)" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 14:32:43 GMT" tweetId="1403721935373144069" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1403721935373144069" inReplyToId="1403721934433554440" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
